data.description:
Come home to the Hill Country! Come out and see this great 2.83 acre property just 7 miles south of hwy 46 in New Braunfels. Beautiful mature hardwoods throughout the property.There is an unfinished 1.5 bath, two-story shop on the property with a well. There are multiple potential home sites for you to build with the option to live in the shop in the meantime. Great price in an awesome neighborhood, lots of potential, just needs a little TLC. There is no HOA.

Please avoid walking into the outbuildings as they are not in good shape and are dangerous.
